'''2014年莫斯科校园枪击案'''发生于2014年2月3日，[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[莫斯科|莫斯科]][[奥特拉德诺耶|奥特拉德诺耶]]{{link-ru|第263中学 (莫斯科)|Школа № 263 (Москва)|第263中学}}15岁的高中生谢尔盖·戈尔杰耶夫（{{lang-ru|Сергей Гордеев}}）开枪打死一名教师后并将29名学生劫为人质后，各打伤或打死一名警察，并向警方自首<ref>Sukhov, Oleg and Matthew Bodner. "[http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/first-ever-school-shooting-prompts-debate-on-security/493765.html First-Ever School Shooting Prompts Debate on Security] {{Wayback|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/first-ever-school-shooting-prompts-debate-on-security/493765.html |date=20140327102233 }}." ''[[The_Moscow_Times|The Moscow Times]]''. February 3, 2014. Retrieved on March 22, 2014. "Police officers evacuating children from School No. 263 in the Otradnoye district in northeast Moscow on Monday after a shooting at there."</ref>。

==事发==
上午11：40许，戈尔杰耶夫穿着大衣，用袋子装着警察上校父亲的Tikka T3步枪和日式BAR M1918小口径[[勃朗宁自动步枪|勃朗宁自动步枪]]上学<ref>{{cite web|title=Student shoots, kills two at Moscow high school  http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-moscow-school-shooting-20140204,0,2381291.story#ixzz2sMivS9nT|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-moscow-school-shooting-20140204,0,2381291.story#axzz2sMi0QMgy|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2014-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422114617/http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-moscow-school-shooting-20140204,0,2381291.story#axzz2sMi0QMgy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Школьник Сергей прятал оружие под шубой|url=http://www.ntv.ru/novosti/838024/|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2014-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140807154413/http://www.ntv.ru/novosti/838024/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Khazov-Kasia|first=Sergey|title=Школьный стрелок|url=http://www.newtimes.ru/articles/detail/78396/|newspaper=The New Times (Russia)|date=2014-02-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221144023/http://www.newtimes.ru/articles/detail/78396/|archivedate=2014-02-21|accessdate=2014-07-18}}</ref>。他胁迫保安，前往地理课堂向他的29岁老师安德烈·基里洛夫（{{lang-ru|Андрей Кириллов}}）的腹部开枪，看到他还活着，又朝其头部开出致命一枪<ref name="rt.com"/>。杀害基里洛夫后，他将班上29名学生劫为人质<ref>{{cite web|title=Student gunman kills 2, briefly takes hostages at Russian school|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/02/03/gunman-kills-2-briefly-takes-hostages-at-russian-school/|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007035958/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2014/02/03/gunman-kills-2-briefly-takes-hostages-at-russian-school/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。戈尔杰耶夫随后向驻校警察开枪，38岁的准尉谢尔盖·布舒耶夫和29岁的高级警长弗拉基米尔·克鲁辛中弹。布舒耶夫送院后不治身亡，克鲁辛肩膀中弹<ref name="rt.com"/><ref>{{cite web|title=Student shoots, kills two at Moscow high school|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-moscow-school-shooting-20140204,0,2381291.story#axzz2sMi0QMgy|accessdate=2014-07-18|archive-date=2014-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422114617/http://www.latimes.com/world/worldnow/la-fg-wn-moscow-school-shooting-20140204,0,2381291.story#axzz2sMi0QMgy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Moscow teen kills two in rare Russian school shooting">{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/03/us-russia-shooting-school-idUSBREA120C920140203 |title="Moscow teen kills two in rare Russian school shooting" |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archive-date=2014-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712011908/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/02/03/us-russia-shooting-school-idUSBREA120C920140203 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

特种部队一小时后抵达现场。戈尔杰耶夫起初打电话给母亲，随后其父亲被特种部队叫来谈判。父亲跟儿子通了15分钟电话后，穿着防弹衣亲自来到学校。30分钟后，戈尔杰耶夫释放人质。下午1：00左右，戈尔杰耶夫向当局自首后被抓获。有报告指出，戈尔杰耶夫在枪击案期间共开出11枪<ref name="rt.com"/><ref name="Moscow teen kills two in rare Russian school shooting"/><ref name="Two dead after gunman takes students hostage in Moscow school">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/02/03/world/europe/russia-school-shooting/ |title="Two dead after gunman takes students hostage in Moscow school" |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606220842/http://www.cnn.com/2014/02/03/world/europe/russia-school-shooting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==反应 ==
[[俄罗斯总统|俄罗斯总统]][[弗拉基米尔·普京|弗拉基米尔·普京]]称该事件为悲剧，要求每个人关注儿童教育和[[枪支管制|枪支管制]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metro.us/boston/news/international/2014/02/03/after-deadly-moscow-school-shooting-putin-calls-for-emphasis-on-culture/ |title=After deadly Moscow school shooting, Putin calls for emphasis on culture |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222163934/http://www.metro.us/boston/news/international/2014/02/03/after-deadly-moscow-school-shooting-putin-calls-for-emphasis-on-culture/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他还告诉莫斯科[[克里姆林宫|克里姆林宫]]艺术文化顾问委员会：“新一代……需要有良好审美能力，理解并重视戏剧、音乐和美术能力的提升。”也有批评也指责接触[[美国文化|美国文化]]和暴力电子游戏<ref name="Moscow teen kills two in rare Russian school shooting"/>。[[莫斯科市长|莫斯科市长]][[谢尔盖·谢苗诺维奇·苏比雅宁|谢尔盖·谢苗诺维奇·苏比雅宁]]随后表示，莫斯科学校已进行安全检查<ref name="rt.com"/>。

== 肇事者 ==
15岁的第263中学学生谢尔盖·戈尔杰耶夫被确认为枪击案肇事者。他是为全A学生，以优异成绩毕业，是全校学生学习的“模范学生”，为人很“内敛”。据称，他与向妨碍他毕业的地理老师发生冲突。最初有报道称遇害地理老师非安德烈·基里洛夫，但其后来被认定是与戈尔杰耶夫发生冲突的老师<ref name="rt.com"/><ref name="Moscow teen kills two in rare Russian school shooting"/><ref name="Two dead after gunman takes students hostage in Moscow school"/><ref name="Student With Rifles Kills 2 in Standoff at Moscow School">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/04/world/europe/fatal-shooting-by-student-at-moscow-school.html?_r=0 |title="Student With Rifles Kills 2 in Standoff at Moscow School" |accessdate=2014-07-18 |archive-date=2014-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027001841/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/04/world/europe/fatal-shooting-by-student-at-moscow-school.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[俄罗斯调查委员会|俄罗斯调查委员会]]发言人弗拉基米尔·马尔表示，戈尔杰耶夫患有[[情绪障碍|情绪障碍]]，他的同学表示，他之前跟其他老师和学生没有明显的冲突<ref name="Student With Rifles Kills 2 in Standoff at Moscow School"/><ref>{{cite web|title=After deadly Moscow school shooting, Putin calls for emphasis on culture - See more at: http://www.metro.us/boston/news/international/2014/02/03/after-deadly-moscow-school-shooting-putin-calls-for-emphasis-on-culture/#sthash.Rb7PDnqz.dpuf|url=http://www.metro.us/boston/news/international/2014/02/03/after-deadly-moscow-school-shooting-putin-calls-for-emphasis-on-culture/|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222163934/http://www.metro.us/boston/news/international/2014/02/03/after-deadly-moscow-school-shooting-putin-calls-for-emphasis-on-culture/|archivedate=2014-02-22|accessdate=2014-07-18}}</ref>。

